# Assets Loans And Receivables Term Net Write Off Amount

## identifier
de7631

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of term loans held by the reporting party which have been written-off during the relevant period. This is net of any amounts recovered from previously written-off term loans that were subsequently recovered during the period.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.TermNetWriteOff.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.05
- period=duration
